<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;MEDSTAR GEORGETOWN UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"MedStar Georgetown University Hospital is a not-for-profit, acute care teaching and research facility located in the Georgetown neighborhood of the Northwest Quadrant of Washington, D.C., affiliated with Georgetown University School of Medicine, and home to the Lombardi Comprehensive Cancer Center and centers of excellence in various medical fields."&lt;SEP&gt;"MedStar Georgetown University Hospital is a not-for-profit, acute care teaching and research facility located in the Georgetown neighborhood of the Northwest Quadrant of Washington, D.C., affiliated with Georgetown University School of Medicine."&lt;SEP&gt;"MedStar Georgetown University Hospital is a not-for-profit, acute care teaching hospital in the national capital area."&lt;SEP&gt;"MedStar Georgetown University Hospital is one of the national capital area's oldest academic teaching hospitals. It is a not-for-profit, acute care teaching hospital."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-10aadd4fba16739e7ec4de021c26c430&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba75b5b3964d44cde7f2dcb299dec0d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f847508265700f6da8b23162b7cfab57</data>
