<node id="&quot;CHILDREN'S NATIONAL MEDICAL CENTER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Children's National Medical Center is a prominent children's hospital located in Washington D.C., ranked among the top 10 in the country."&lt;SEP&gt;"Children's National Medical Center is a top-ranked children's hospital located near McMillan Reservoir and Howard University, sharing grounds with several other medical facilities. It serves as a regional referral center for various pediatric specialties and performs over 450,000 visits annually."&lt;SEP&gt;"Children’s National Medical Center (formerly DC Children’s Hospital) is ranked among the top 10 children’s hospitals in the country by U.S. News &amp; World Report. It is located just north of the Mc area in Washington D.C."</data>
